-- Monte Paschi top investor says has sold 12 pct stake 
-- 
-- Tue Mar 18, 2014 04:04PM EDT
-- None



MILAN, March 18 (Reuters) - The top investor in Banca Monte dei Paschi di Siena <BMPS.MI> sold a 12 percent stake in the bank on Tuesday, it said in a statement.

The Monte dei Paschi foundation said it now had a stake of 15.07 percent in the bank, following further share sales on the market on Tuesday and in previous days.